@startuml harness-flow
title brew-mgt — Harness Operating Flow (per session)

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ArrowColor #444444
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor #F4F6F8
  BorderColor #5B6B7B
  DiamondBackgroundColor #FFF3E0
  DiamondBorderColor #D95C41
}

|#E8F0FE|Session Start|
start
:Run ./init.sh
(build CLI, init/refresh harness.db,
feature sync, baseline verify, enable hooks);
if (Baseline verification passes?) then (no)
  #FFE0E0:STOP — fix the baseline first;
  stop
else (yes)
endif
:Read claude-progress.md + session-handoff.md;
:Read feature_list.json
-> pick highest-priority NON-passing feature;

|#FFF8E1|Task Loop|
:Classify request with docs/FEATURE_INTAKE.md
(lane = tiny | normal | high-risk);
:harness-cli intake --type --summary --lane;
:Mark feature in_progress in feature_list.json
-> harness-cli feature sync;
:Check proof status
-> harness-cli query matrix;

if (Lane = high-risk?) then (yes)
  :Write decision record
docs/decisions/NNNN.md
+ harness-cli decision add;
  if (Human confirms?) then (no)
    #FFE0E0:Pause — await human decision;
    stop
  else (yes)
  endif
else (no)
endif

:Do the work IN-LANE
(follow sops/layered-domain-architecture.md);

:Produce a PRODUCT delta and/or HARNESS delta
- PRODUCT: app code, tests, API, product docs
- HARNESS: docs, templates, backlog, decisions;

:Run validation / proofs for the feature;
if (Proofs pass with evidence?) then (yes)
  :Record evidence in feature_list.json
mark passing -> harness-cli feature sync;
else (no)
  :Keep status in_progress / blocked
record the blocker;
endif

:Ask: did product truth, validation,
architecture, failure patterns, or
next-agent instructions change?;
:Encode new knowledge
(sops/encode-unseen-knowledge.md);
:harness-cli trace --summary --outcome --story;
if (Harness friction found?) then (yes)
  :harness-cli backlog add  (or fix it directly);
else (no)
endif

|#E8F5E9|Session End — leave a clean state|
:Run clean-state-checklist.md;
:Update claude-progress.md + session-handoff.md;
:Ensure feature_list.json is honest
-> harness-cli feature sync;
:Self-review with evaluator-rubric.md;
:Update quality-document.md (codebase health);
:git commit
(pre-commit hook: validate feature_list + feature sync);
stop

@enduml
